As recorded by Jimi Hendrix
(From the 2002 Album BLUE WILD ANGEL: LIVE AT THE ISLE OF WIGHT)

Words and Music by John Lennon &amp; Paul McCartney
Arranged by Jimi Hendrix

Transcribed by Slowhand


